abstract: President Donald Trump will sign an executive order on Wednesday targeting antisemitism on college campuses, the White House said.
snippet: President Donald Trump will sign an executive order on Wednesday targeting antisemitism on college campuses, the White House said.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Donald Trump will sign an executive order on Wednesday targeting antisemitism on college campuses, the White House said.
headline_main: Trump to Sign Order Targeting Anti-Semitism at Colleges
headline_print_headline: Trump to Sign Order Targeting Anti-Semitism at Colleges

abstract: For the House progressives:  a pair of impeachment articles against President Donald Trump. For the vulnerable Democratic freshmen: charges that are narrowly focused on Ukraine. And for the whole House Democratic majority — and, however backhandedly, Trump himself: a sweeping new trade deal.
snippet: For the House progressives:  a pair of impeachment articles against President Donald Trump. For the vulnerable Democratic freshmen: charges that are narrowly focused on Ukraine. And for the whole House Democratic majority — and, however backhanded...
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — For the House progressives: a pair of impeachment articles against President Donald Trump. For the vulnerable Democratic freshmen: charges that are narrowly focused on Ukraine. And for the whole House Democratic majority — and, however backhandedly, Trump himself: a sweeping new trade deal.
headline_main: Pelosi Offers Some Trade Policy With That Impeachment
headline_print_headline: Pelosi Offers Some Trade Policy With That Impeachment

abstract: An energetic leader, he steered the Russian capital out of its gloom, dominating Moscow’s political system while his wife became the richest woman in the country.
snippet: An energetic leader, he steered the Russian capital out of its gloom, dominating Moscow’s political system while his wife became the richest woman in the country.
lead_paragraph: MOSCOW — Yuri M. Luzhkov, who as the city’s longtime mayor led the transformation of Moscow from a gloomy, trash-strewn post-Soviet capital into a gleaming modern metropolis, but who was dogged by allegations that he had helped enrich his wife’s construction company, died on Tuesday in Munich. He was 83.

abstract: How does Trump’s attorney general keep a straight face?
snippet: How does Trump’s attorney general keep a straight face?
lead_paragraph: Donald Trump famously said that he could shoot somebody in the middle of Fifth Avenue and not “lose any voters.” I don’t know about that. But I’m confident that he wouldn’t lose Bill Barr.

abstract: Britain's election race has tightened markedly over the past two weeks and Prime Minister Boris Johnson is now likely to win only a modest majority in Thursday's vote, according to a closely watched forecast released on Tuesday.
snippet: Britain's election race has tightened markedly over the past two weeks and Prime Minister Boris Johnson is now likely to win only a modest majority in Thursday's vote, according to a closely watched forecast released on Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — Britain's election race has tightened markedly over the past two weeks and Prime Minister Boris Johnson is now likely to win only a modest majority in Thursday's vote, according to a closely watched forecast released on Tuesday.
headline_main: UK's Johnson Now Less Certain of Election Victory: YouGov
headline_print_headline: UK's Johnson Now Less Certain of Election Victory: YouGov

abstract: Rudy Giuliani, President Donald Trump’s personal attorney, said Tuesday that the president asked him to brief the Justice Department and Republican senators on the findings of his recent trip to Ukraine.
snippet: Rudy Giuliani, President Donald Trump’s personal attorney, said Tuesday that the president asked him to brief the Justice Department and Republican senators on the findings of his recent trip to Ukraine.
lead_paragraph: NEW YORK — Rudy Giuliani, President Donald Trump’s personal attorney, said Tuesday that the president asked him to brief the Justice Department and Republican senators on the findings of his recent trip to Ukraine.
headline_main: Giuliani Indicates He'll Report on Ukraine Trip This Week
headline_print_headline: Giuliani Indicates He'll Report on Ukraine Trip This Week

abstract: While many American officials are eager to avoid the new tariffs, the president could go either way.
snippet: While many American officials are eager to avoid the new tariffs, the president could go either way.
lead_paragraph: New tariffs on over $100 billion of Chinese goods are due to take effect on Sunday, but the Trump administration is sending mixed signals on delaying them as the United States and China keep haggling over a trade deal.

abstract: Pretrial proceedings revealed the couple’s $230,000 monthly spending, which enabled $12,000 splurges for cigars and $7,000 for fountain pens.

lead_paragraph: The acrimonious divorce case of Rudolph W. Giuliani and his estranged wife, Judith, a battle that had played out in court and across tabloid headlines for more than a year and a half, came to an abrupt — and harmonious — end on Tuesday evening, according to her lawyer.

abstract: Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro issued a decree on Tuesday that will allow tens of thousands of small farmer to finally gain title to the land they cultivate, making good on a campaign promise to the farm sector that backed his election.
snippet: Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro issued a decree on Tuesday that will allow tens of thousands of small farmer to finally gain title to the land they cultivate, making good on a campaign promise to the farm sector that backed his election.
lead_paragraph: BRASILIA — Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro issued a decree on Tuesday that will allow tens of thousands of small farmer to finally gain title to the land they cultivate, making good on a campaign promise to the farm sector that backed his election.
headline_main: Brazil's Bolsonaro Moves on Land Titles for Small Farmers
headline_print_headline: Brazil's Bolsonaro Moves on Land Titles for Small Farmers
